---
layout: base.njk
title: Guías de visas y trámites migratorios para colombianos
description: Guías claras y actualizadas sobre visas y trámites migratorios para colombianos que quieren viajar, estudiar o trabajar en EEUU y Canadá.
---
{% from "icons.njk" import categoryIcon %}
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-text">
    <h1>Guías de trámites y visas</h1>
    <p>Explicaciones claras, basadas en fuentes oficiales, para colombianos que
    están tramitando una visa o un documento migratorio hacia Estados Unidos o
    Canadá.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-art" aria-hidden="true">
    <svg viewBox="0 0 240 200" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
      <rect x="30" y="60" width="110" height="120" rx="14" fill="#1f5fbf"/>
      <rect x="42" y="74" width="86" height="92" rx="8" fill="#eaf1fc"/>
      <circle cx="85" cy="110" r="16" fill="#ffffff" stroke="#1f5fbf" stroke-width="4"/>
      <path d="M77 110l6 6 12-14" fill="none" stroke="#1f5fbf" stroke-width="4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
      <rect x="58" y="138" width="54" height="6" rx="3" fill="#b9cdec"/>
      <rect x="58" y="150" width="38" height="6" rx="3" fill="#b9cdec"/>

      <g transform="rotate(-8 170 68)">
        <rect x="130" y="40" width="80" height="56" rx="10" fill="#ffffff" stroke="#e2e8f0" stroke-width="2"/>
        <line x1="168" y1="46" x2="168" y2="90" stroke="#e2e8f0" stroke-width="2" stroke-dasharray="4 4"/>
        <rect x="138" y="50" width="22" height="6" rx="3" fill="#ffb020"/>
        <rect x="138" y="62" width="22" height="4" rx="2" fill="#c7d3e0"/>
        <rect x="138" y="70" width="18" height="4" rx="2" fill="#c7d3e0"/>
        <circle cx="188" cy="68" r="10" fill="#eaf1fc"/>
      </g>

      <g transform="translate(148 14) rotate(25)">
        <path d="M0 14 L34 0 L18 14 L34 28 Z" fill="#ffb020"/>
      </g>
      <path d="M118 28 Q140 8 162 16" fill="none" stroke="#ffb020" stroke-width="2" stroke-dasharray="3 5" stroke-linecap="round"/>

      <g transform="translate(168 108) scale(1.3)">
        <path d="M12 2C7.6 2 4 5.6 4 10c0 6 8 14 8 14s8-8 8-14c0-4.4-3.6-8-8-8z" fill="#ff6b57"/>
        <circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3.4" fill="#ffffff"/>
      </g>
    </svg>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="filters">
  <input type="search" id="search-input" placeholder="Busca un tema: apostilla, DS-160, remesas..." aria-label="Buscar artículos">
  <div class="filter-pills" role="group" aria-label="Filtrar por categoría">
    <button type="button" class="pill active" data-filter="all">Todos</button>
    {% for cat in collections.categories %}
    <button type="button" class="pill" data-filter="{{ cat }}">{{ cat }}</button>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</div>

<ul class="article-list">
  {% for post in collections.articulos %}
  <li class="article-card" data-category="{{ post.data.category }}">
    <a class="article-card-link" href="{{ post.url }}">
      <span class="icon-bubble">{{ categoryIcon(post.data.category) }}</span>
      <span class="badge">{{ post.data.category }}</span>
      <h2>{{ post.data.title }}</h2>
      <p>{{ post.data.description }}</p>
    </a>
  </li>
  {% endfor %}
</ul>
<p class="no-results" hidden>No encontramos artículos con ese criterio. Prueba con otra palabra o categoría.</p>
